		<description><![CDATA[<p><img align="right" class="alignright size-medium wp-image-4146" src="http://www.makealivingwriting.com/wp-content/uploads/photodune-5630330-blogging-concept-xs-300x199.jpg" alt="Blogging concept" width="300" height="199" /></p>
<p>You may think this is a funny piece of advice for me to write on my blog.</p>
<p>But if you care about earning more as a freelance writer, then you might want to stop writing blog posts.</p>
<p>Why do I say this?</p>
<p>There are four big reasons I want to steer you away from blogging:</p>
<div class="read-more"><a href="http://www.makealivingwriting.com/stop-writing-blog-posts-do-this-instead/">Read more &#8250;</a></div>
<p><!-- end of .read-more --></p>
